# Package Boundaries

## Dependency direction

```
apps/h5, apps/web  →  @ryx/api, @ryx/ui, @ryx/shared-types
@ryx/api           →  @ryx/shared-types
@ryx/ui            →  (peer: react, react-dom)
```

- Apps must not import from each other
- `packages/api` must not import React or app code
- `packages/ui` must not import `@ryx/api`

## Adding dependencies

- Shared runtime dep → add to the package that uses it
- Workspace link → `"@ryx/foo": "workspace:*"`
- Before adding/updating deps → `pnpm audit`

## shadcn/ui

- Install components into `packages/ui`, not apps
- Keep `components.json` aliases consistent across ui + apps
- After `shadcn add`, verify `globals.css` `@source` still covers all apps
